data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Escondido at Tres Lagos! This stunning 2-story residence offers both elegance and comfort, you'll enjoy unparalleled access to top-tier schools, parks, walking trails and recreational opportunities!  The open-concept layout on the main floor seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an inviting space for both entertaining and everyday living. 4 bedrooms and 2 baths. With a generous 1,984 square feet of living space, this pearl was thoughtfully constructed in 2021. The backyard, offers the perfect backdrop for outdoor gatherings or tranquil relaxation. Don't miss your chance to own a piece of contemporary luxury in a community that embraces education, nature, and recreation. Your new chapter begins here, at Escondido at Tres Lagos. VERY MOTIVATED SELLER! Schedule your tour today!
